fm: int strStr(string &haystack, string &needle) {         int n = haystack.size(), m = needle.size();         if (m == 0)             return 0;         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             if (i + m > n)                 return -1;             int j = 0;             while (j < m && haystack[i + j] == needle[j])                 ++j;             if (j == m)                 return i;         }         return -1;     }
